column2: SELECT Bucket, COUNT (*) AS Count FROM (SELECT (z - (SELECT MIN (z) FROM SpecObj WHERE class = # AND zWarning = # and survey = #) ) as Bottom, CAST ((z - (SELECT MIN (z) FROM SpecObj WHERE class = # AND zWarning = # and survey = #) ) / ( ((SELECT MAX (z) *# FROM SpecObj WHERE class = # AND zWarning = # and survey = #) - (SELECT MIN (z) FROM SpecObj WHERE class = # AND zWarning = # and survey = #) ) / #) AS INT) + # as Bucket FROM SpecObj WHERE class = # AND zWarning = # and survey = #) a GROUP BY Bucket ORDER BY Bucket
